&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage complex calendars, scheduling meetings, events, and calls across multiple time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritize requests and ensure the CEO’s time is allocated to the highest-value activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare meeting materials, agendas, presentations, and follow-up summaries.&lt;/li&gt;
