&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are hiring a Geotechnical Engineer to help accelerate our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Geotechnical Engineer will be responsible for providing geotechnical expertise to support the safe and efficient design, operation, and monitoring of underground mining activities. This role involves assessing ground conditions, designing support systems, conducting stability analyses, and ensuring compliance with geotechnical standards and mining regulations. The Geotechnical Engineer will report to Lead Geotechnical Engineer and will work closely with mine planning, geology, hydrology, Safety and operations teams to mitigate geotechnical risks and optimize production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ground Control &amp;amp; Stability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct rock mass characterization (RMR, Q-System, GSI, RQD) and develop geotechnical models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform stope, drift, shaft, and pillar stability analyses using empirical methods and numerical modelling (Map3D, FLAC3D).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, specify, and optimize ground support systems (bolts, cable bolts, shotcrete, mesh, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and assess performance of excavations and ground support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Geotechnical Data Collection &amp;amp; Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Log core and map underground exposures to identify structures, discontinuities, and rock mass conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install and interpret geotechnical instrumentation (extensometers, stress cells, convergence monitoring, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain geotechnical databases and records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor Geotechnical compliance on shaft sinking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mine Planning &amp;amp; Risk Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide geotechnical input into short-, medium-, and long-term mine designs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct risk assessments for potential ground control hazards.&lt;/li&gt

