&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify data gaps in the hydrogeology program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and lead field teams to execute these data collection programs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical and administrative support to hydrogeologic field operations in support of mine area surface and groundwater management strategies, including piezometric completions, drill stem injection test, other monitoring and characterization tests&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
